  "description": "<h2><u>Project engineer, electrical x2</u></h2>\n<p><strong>Need Engrg Jobs?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Visit: https://www.ourengineers.com</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support the Manager in project planning and site coordination.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and revise engineering documents, drawings, and safety procedures.</li>\n  <li>Issue final specifications and bills of materials for purchase orders; negotiate with vendors and subcontractors.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely delivery of goods and equipment by liaising with vendors and subcontractors.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and supervise construction teams for installation, testing, and commissioning of equipment.</li>\n  <li>Communicate with consultants, owners, and authorities regarding engineering requests.</li>\n  <li>Plan and schedule site activities according to the master program, ensuring safety and timeliness.</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc duties as assigned by management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Degree / Diploma /NITEC with experience.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Post OPEN to SINGAPOREAN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Need Engrg Jobs?</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Visit: https://www.ourengineers.com</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
